# mostly taken from https://docs.docker.com/compose/django/
FROM python:3.10
ENV PYTHONUNBUFFERED 1 
RUN mkdir /config 
ADD requirements.txt /config/
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r /config/requirements.txt
RUN mkdir /src; 
WORKDIR /src
